What is your overall assessment of this course?
Do you expect to use this class for credit toward your major, or toward a pre-professional program?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: May or may not improve in the coming years. This year, conversation was incredibly slow at times. Could have been the students' fault, but the professor also tended to ask broad, weighty questions that made everyone afraid to say anything. The concept is interesting though.
The worst class of my undergrad career at Yale. It was terrible. She turns on her charm and lures you in during shopping period. Don't fall for it. The class is terrible. So glad it's done.
